01:18:44.040 --> 01:18:46.040
[Guest 2]: that happens from one person to another.

01:18:46.040 --> 01:18:49.040
[Guest 2]: It is not that I came to you with a bottle of wine.

01:18:49.040 --> 01:18:51.040
[Guest 2]: If you haven't thought about it,

01:18:51.040 --> 01:18:54.040
[Guest 2]: and you haven't brought the correct gift for it,

01:18:54.040 --> 01:18:56.040
[Guest 2]: then your gift has no value.

01:18:56.040 --> 01:18:58.040
[Guest 2]: These are the values that he taught me.

01:18:58.040 --> 01:19:00.040
[Guest 2]: What a great perspective.

01:19:00.040 --> 01:19:03.040
[Guest 2]: He's saying, my job is to make people happy.

