01:19:07.040 --> 01:19:10.040
[Guest 2]: And because you said it, now you know why.

01:19:11.040 --> 01:19:14.040
[Amit Varma]: And everything you've told Roshan about him is false.

01:19:14.040 --> 01:19:16.040
[Guest 1]: Just to make him happy.

01:19:18.040 --> 01:19:23.040
