01:19:23.040 --> 01:19:27.040
[Guest 2]: and says that, Vikram, gift value is not important.

01:19:27.040 --> 01:19:31.040
[Guest 2]: He said, this small purse I gave to the media manager at Wimbledon,

01:19:31.040 --> 01:19:35.040
[Guest 2]: I'm just watching Roger Federer live at Centre Court.

01:19:35.040 --> 01:19:39.040
[Guest 2]: So what I learned from him is that this guilt of making other people happy

01:19:39.040 --> 01:19:43.040
[Guest 2]: and feel important, why am I living with this?

01:19:43.040 --> 01:19:45.040
[Guest 2]: On the contrary, I should develop this skill,

01:19:45.040 --> 01:19:49.040
[Guest 2]: whether it is helpful in business or whether it's helpful in life,

01:19:49.040 --> 01:19:50.040
[Amit Varma]: it does not matter.

01:19:50.040 --> 01:19:51.040
[Amit Varma]: But do it for his own sake.

01:19:51.040 --> 01:19:52.040
[Guest 2]: Do it for his own sake.

01:19:52.040 --> 01:19:54.040
[Guest 2]: Because his life is, I mean, charity.

01:19:54.040 --> 01:19:56.040
[Guest 2]: Today we are giving millions of dollars for people's upliftment.

01:19:56.040 --> 01:19:58.040
[Guest 2]: Just be nice to them.

01:19:58.040 --> 01:20:01.040
[Guest 2]: Just do a little bit of an act which makes them happy.

01:20:01.040 --> 01:20:03.040
[Guest 2]: And that changed my perspective.

01:20:03.040 --> 01:20:06.040
[Guest 2]: And I realized that I don't do one-tenth of what he does.

01:20:06.040 --> 01:20:08.040
