[Guest 2]: What do I do now?

02:35:15.960 --> 02:35:17.960
[Guest 2]: I am enjoying here.

02:35:17.960 --> 02:35:19.960
[Guest 2]: And that's where I think it's my fault that I didn't push myself.

02:35:19.960 --> 02:35:21.960
[Guest 2]: I could have probably got

02:35:21.960 --> 02:35:23.960
[Guest 2]: 6 or 8 specials by now.

02:35:23.960 --> 02:35:25.960
[Guest 2]: Because I had so much of material gathered over a period of time.

02:35:27.960 --> 02:35:29.960
[Guest 2]: But then this interested me more.

02:35:29.960 --> 02:35:31.960
[Guest 2]: And then this journey started.

02:35:31.960 --> 02:35:33.960
[Guest 2]: Which led to what the duck might show.

02:35:33.960 --> 02:35:35.960
[Guest 2]: And as we go further,

02:35:35.960 --> 02:35:37.960
[Guest 2]: I will probably break down on various

02:35:37.960 --> 02:35:39.960
[Guest 2]: special qualities of the

02:35:39.960 --> 02:35:41.960
[Guest 2]: sports people that I saw.

02:35:41.960 --> 02:35:43.960
[Guest 2]: And probably put it in context of

02:35:43.960 --> 02:35:45.960
[Guest 2]: what is that one thing I learnt out of those players.

02:35:45.960 --> 02:35:47.960
[Guest 2]: But this journey

02:35:47.960 --> 02:35:49.960
[Guest 2]: of unravelling a high performance athlete

02:35:49.960 --> 02:35:51.960
[Guest 2]: was the best thing I experienced

02:35:51.960 --> 02:35:53.960
[Amit Varma]: in my life.

