[Amit Varma]: to take it into other directions

02:36:27.960 --> 02:36:29.960
[Amit Varma]: which could also have been rewarding for you.

02:36:29.960 --> 02:36:31.960
[Amit Varma]: And I am thinking in terms of creators.

02:36:31.960 --> 02:36:33.960
[Amit Varma]: These are choices

02:36:33.960 --> 02:36:35.960
[Amit Varma]: all creators are confronted with at some point

02:36:35.960 --> 02:36:37.960
[Amit Varma]: in time. You can take your work

02:36:37.960 --> 02:36:39.960
[Amit Varma]: in one direction or you can

02:36:39.960 --> 02:36:41.960
[Amit Varma]: take it into the other direction.

02:36:41.960 --> 02:36:43.960
[Amit Varma]: And you make a choice. And that choice changes

02:36:43.960 --> 02:36:45.960
[Amit Varma]: what you do. And then what you do changes

