03:29:37.960 --> 03:29:39.960
[Amit Varma]: the Twitter quote tweet for the kind of

03:29:39.960 --> 03:29:41.960
[Amit Varma]: rudeness and interactions it encourages.

03:29:41.960 --> 03:29:43.960
[Amit Varma]: What it has done is that it has

03:29:43.960 --> 03:29:45.960
[Amit Varma]: amplified the worst aspects of

03:29:45.960 --> 03:29:47.960
[Amit Varma]: our character. The

03:29:47.960 --> 03:29:49.960
